comments.body: Yeah, I don't know what is with the name.  I couldn't find *just* the species here on iNat.
Is the name in error? It has a genus, and then a subspecies.

results.description: In a pile of pine logs at an outdoor sawmill.  Identification confirmed by Ted MacRae, a recognized authority on Cerambycidae.
